OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FNearly 20 years on from the original
OL,7,FCorby toxic waste scandal, more than
OL,8,F100 additional people have come
OL,9,Fforward with concerns that they too
OL,10,Fhave suffered birth defects, as
OL,11,Frevealed by a 15-month investigation
OL,12,Fby ITV News Reporter Amy Lewis
OL,14,FWhen a landmark High Court case ruled
OL,15,Fnegligence had caused birth defects in
OL,16,F18 children, we thought we knew the
OL,17,Ffull horror of Corby's toxic fallout.
OL,19,FBut now more than 100 people have come
OL,20,Fforward, believing they were also
OL,21,Faffected by the scandal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FIn 2009, Corby Borough Council was
OL,7,Ffound to have negligently moved toxic
OL,8,Fwaste from the Northamptonshire town's
OL,9,Fmain former steelworks.
OL,11,FHowever, over the course of a 15-month
OL,12,FITV News investigation, 105 people
OL,13,Faffected by birth defects who were not
OL,14,Finvolved in the original case have
OL,15,Fshared their concerns about the impact
OL,16,Fthe waste has had on their health.
OL,18,FTracey Taylor's daughter, Shelby-Anne,
OL,19,Fdied when she was four days old in
OL,20,F1996 from heart, lung, kidney and ear
OL,21,Fdefects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FTracey worked alongside the
OL,7,Freclamation six days a week when she
OL,8,Fwas pregnant. She has been collecting
OL,9,Fand collating questionnaires from
OL,10,Ffamilies with babies born with defects
OL,11,For babies who didn't survive because
OL,12,Fof organ defects, which she describes
OL,13,Fas 'angel babies'.
OL,15,FIt is part of her campaign for a
OL,16,Fpublic inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "It is
OL,7,Fheartbreaking to see that there are so
OL,8,Fmany. I always knew that there were
OL,9,Fmore families affected than those in
OL,10,Fthe original case, but to actually be
OL,11,Fat 105 with limb differences and angel
OL,12,Fbabies, it's heartbreaking."
OL,14,FTwenty-four of the families who have
OL,15,Ffilled in questionnaires have hand
OL,16,Fdefects - more than the total number
OL,17,Finvolved in the original court case.
OL,26,@nD@TOUtD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
