OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FIssy Wright, 25, began questioning if
OL,7,Fshe was missing a finger and thumb on
OL,8,Fboth her hands because of Corby's
OL,9,Fcontaminated waste when she watched
OL,10,FToxic Town last year, a Netflix drama
OL,11,Fseries about Corby's toxic past.
OL,13,FIssy told ITV News: "I have three
OL,14,Ffingers on each hand, and my arms
OL,15,Fdon't straighten properly. They're
OL,16,Falso slightly shorter than they should
OL,17,Fbe. I've got a curvature in my spine
OL,18,Fand a small heart murmur as well. I've
OL,19,Fgrown up very physically different to
OL,20,Fother people."
OL,26,@uD@UOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FShe adds, "It's affected me a lot
OL,7,Fmentally and physically and yes,
OL,8,Fcontinues to, it never goes away."
OL,10,FHer mother, Pippa, grew up around
OL,11,FCorby during the reclamation of the
OL,12,Fsteelworks. She told ITV News that she
OL,13,Fdidn't know about her daughter's
OL,14,Fconditions until she was born, adding:
OL,15,F"The general questions were, did you
OL,16,Flive near toxic waste or were you
OL,17,Frelated to her father.
OL,26,@nD@KOUpD@bO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
