OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,F"The answer to both of those was no...
OL,7,FThe toxic waste just seems to be the
OL,8,Fplausible explanation really because
OL,9,Fwe don't have any history of this in
OL,10,Fthe family. We've had so much genetic
OL,11,Ftesting through the NHS that just
OL,12,Fhasn't ever come up with any
OL,13,Fconclusion of what caused it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
