OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FThe council has only ever admitted
OL,7,Fdumping the waste at Deene Quarry, a
OL,8,Fformer landfill site on the outskirts
OL,9,Fof the town. It was later developed
OL,10,Finto Rockingham Speedway, which shut
OL,11,Fin 2018. Families are concerned that
OL,12,Fthe historical waste is still causing
OL,13,Fproblems to this day.
OL,15,FITV News can reveal that 19 incidents
OL,16,Frelated to contaminated water and
OL,17,Funidentified pollution around Deene
OL,18,FQuarry have been reported to the
OL,19,FEnvironment Agency in the last decade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FOne incident report from 2024 obtained
OL,7,Fby ITV News under the Freedom of
OL,8,FInformation Act states, "There were
OL,9,Falso patches of a thick red material
OL,10,Fclinging to the sides of the
OL,11,Fwatercourse in a number of discrete
OL,12,Fpatches."
OL,14,FAnother reported noticeable water
OL,15,Fdiscolouration "with rust red scum".
OL,16,FFamilies repeatedly reported seeing
OL,17,Fred dust during the reclamation during
OL,18,Fthe original High Court case.
OL,26,@pD@YOUtD@IO]wD@POUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
