PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FThe documents also show that
OL,7,F'reputational issues' such as 'public,
OL,8,Fpolitical and media interest' were the
OL,9,Freason for attending one of the
OL,10,Fincidents. The report states: "As you
OL,11,Fare aware there is continued public
OL,12,Fawareness and interest surrounding
OL,13,Fpollutants to the Gretton brook and
OL,14,Fwider area."
OL,16,FAlso, contaminated waste from the
OL,17,Fformer steelworks could be leaking
OL,18,Ffrom the ground, according to details
OL,19,Ffrom a meeting between Gretton Parish
OL,20,FCouncil and the Environment Agency.
OL,26,@rD@_OUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
