OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FA document from the January 2025
OL,7,Fmeeting states: "Water from the open
OL,8,Flandfill underneath Rockingham
OL,9,FSpeedway is pooling by the side of the
OL,10,FGretton Brook Road... Historically
OL,11,Fwhen Anglian Water went to assess the
OL,12,Fsites at Rockingham Speedway,
OL,13,Fattenuation ponds were assessed and
OL,14,Fcleared.
OL,16,F"This suggests that groundwater levels
OL,17,Fhave risen and are pushing up the
OL,18,Fhistoric contamination in the ground
OL,19,Fand it is leaking onto the road."
OL,26,@oD@QOUxD@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
