OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FWe showed Professor Mark Hodson, a
OL,7,Fcontaminated soil expert, our
OL,8,Ffindings. He told ITV News:
OL,9,F"Certainly, in the past, the
OL,10,Flegislation around landfills was a lot
OL,11,Fless developed than it is now... What
OL,12,FI haven't read in the reports is any
OL,13,Fsuggestion that the cells where the
OL,14,Fcontaminated waste has been buried are
OL,15,Fthe ones that have been leaking."
OL,17,FHe adds: "However, if I were living in
OL,18,Fthat area I think I would like to see
OL,19,Fmore tests being done just to reassure
OL,20,Fmyself that there wasn't any further
OL,21,Frisk of harm occurring."
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@aO]yD@JOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
