OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FNorth Northamptonshire Council, which
OL,7,Fwas created after Corby Borough
OL,8,FCouncil was abolished, has declined
OL,9,Four request to be interviewed.
OL,11,FHowever, it told ITV News in a written
OL,12,Fstatement that "North Northamptonshire
OL,13,FCouncil recognises the understandable
OL,14,Fstrength of feeling amongst the
OL,15,Fresidents of Corby in relation to the
OL,16,Fhistoric and emotive issue of
OL,17,Fcontaminated land and takes
OL,18,Fenvironmental concerns extremely
OL,19,Fseriously."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FIt adds: "Investigations carried out
OL,7,Fby the Environment Agency and
OL,8,Findependent consultants identified
OL,9,Fthat water entering Gretton Brook is
OL,10,Fassociated with a corroded pipe acting
OL,11,Fas a pathway for surface water or
OL,12,Fgroundwater, rather than confirming
OL,13,Fthat a landfill site is leaking.
OL,15,F"Water quality monitoring undertaken
OL,16,Fin February 2025 identified elevated
OL,17,FpH levels at the point where water
OL,18,Fenters the brook, which is consistent
OL,19,Fwith alkaline water sometimes
OL,20,Fassociated with historic industrial
OL,21,Fland or construction materials.
OL,26,@nD@JOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,F"The monitoring results did not
OL,7,Fidentify heavy metal concentrations
OL,8,Fabove relevant environmental
OL,9,Fstandards. This is consistent with
OL,10,Fannual monitoring of the Deene Quarry
OL,11,Fsite carried out by the Council
OL,12,Fthrough an independent Consultant and
OL,13,Foverseen by the Environment Agency."
OL,15,FThe council also states: "If credible
OL,16,Fevidence emerges indicating a risk to
OL,17,Fhuman health or the environment, the
OL,18,FCouncil and relevant regulators would
OL,19,Freview the information and determine
OL,20,Fwhether further investigation or
OL,21,Faction is required."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@ZOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
