OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FIn January, a report by Earthwatch
OL,7,FEurope found rivers around Corby are
OL,8,Fpolluted with metals that could pose a
OL,9,Frisk to aquatic life.
OL,11,FThe environmental charity and
OL,12,Fvolunteers tested rivers around the
OL,13,Ftown and detected at least one metal
OL,14,For metalloid at a concentration above
OL,15,Fthe level which adversely affects
OL,16,Faquatic ecosystems at each of the 59
OL,17,Fsites they visited.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
