OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAn Environment Agency spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "We recognise the concerns
OL,13,Fraised and understand how important it
OL,14,Fis for residents to feel confident in
OL,15,Fthe quality of their local environment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
