CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779393955
OL,3,CMore than 100 people report birth
OL,4,Cdefects after Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,F"Our initial review of the data in the
OL,7,FCorby Metals Testing Report study does
OL,8,Fnot indicate any significant impact on
OL,9,Fthe freshwater environment but we will
OL,10,Fcontinue to carry out monitoring in
OL,11,Fthe area and work closely with North
OL,12,FNorthamptonshire Council."
OL,14,FIn total, more than 180 people
OL,15,Fconcerned about their health have
OL,16,Ffilled in questionnaires as part of
OL,17,FTracey Taylor's campaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
